  "text": "Inclusion criteria for and participation rate of EYHS are described in detail in a previously published article [CITATION_1] . In brief, the present study population consisted of 3rd grade students of the EYHS study population (n = 589). In 2001, as 6th graders, they made up the study population of adolescents for 'Fyn's Backs'. Participants with missing information on any measurement at baseline (n = 41) and incomplete follow-up (n = 150) were excluded from the analyses. In total, 398 children (181 boys and 217 girls) were eligible for analyses.",
